<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - ONNIEONE News</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; }
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        
        .page-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #dc2626 70%, #ffffff 100%);
            color: white; padding: 60px 0; text-align: center;
        }
        .page-header i { font-size: 50px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .page-header h1 { font-size: 36px; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #dc2626; }
        
        .page-content {
            background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px; margin: 40px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .page-content h2 { color: #1a1a1a; margin: 30px 0 15px; border-bottom: 3px solid #dc2626; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .page-content h3 { color: #dc2626; margin: 20px 0 10px; }
        .page-content p { color: #495057; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .page-content ul { margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .page-content li { color: #495057; margin: 8px 0; }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: #dc2626; color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: #000; transform: translateY(-2px); }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .page-header h1 { font-size: 28px; }
            .page-content { padding: 25px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <div class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
            <h1>About Us</h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="page-content">
            
            <h2>About ONNIEONE NEWS</h2>
            <p>ONNIEONE NEWS is Africa's premier digital news platform, delivering accurate, timely, and comprehensive news coverage from Rwanda, across Africa, and around the world. Founded in 2020, we have grown to become one of the most trusted sources for news in the region.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>To provide reliable, unbiased, and impactful journalism that empowers our readers with the knowledge they need to understand their world and make informed decisions.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>To be Africa's most trusted digital news platform, setting the standard for excellence in journalism and innovation in news delivery.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Values</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> We uphold the highest standards of journalistic ethics.</li>
                <li><strong>Accuracy:</strong> We verify every fact before publication.</li>
                <li><strong>Independence:</strong> We report without fear or favor.</li>
                <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We embrace new technologies to better serve our readers.</li>
            </ul>
        
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>